sect1.para:
The Relevant patches page displays a customized list
of patches applying to your registered systems (see
).

The Package Search page allows you to search through
packages using various criteria provided by the What to search
for selection list:

note.para:
A sandbox icon (
Spacewalk Icon Sandbox
) indicates that the listed file is currently located in a local sandbox. Files in a system's sandbox are considered experimental and could be unstable. Use caution when selecting them for a central configuration channel.
